      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the rice is cooking, boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>spice paste</strong> with the <strong>kaffir lime leaves</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5-6 min, stirring continuously, or until fragrant</p>",
