    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once slightly thickened, add the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lime</strong> with the<strong> jumbo prawns </strong>and cook for a further 4-5 min or until the prawns are cooked through</p><p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> remaining lime</strong> into wedges</p><p>Add the <strong>cooked aubergine</strong> with most of the<strong> coriander leaves</strong> (save some for garnish!) and gently stir it all together – this is your <strong>fiery Thai Kaeng Pa</strong></p>",
